### 3. SystemSettings

Global platform config. Single row. **Does not contain WhatsApp or email credentials** — those live in AdminSettings.

| Field | Type | Notes |
|-------|------|-------|
| `id` | String (cuid) | PK |
| `settings` | JSON? | Platform-level flags and config |
| `updatedAt` | DateTime | Auto |
| `updatedBy` | String? | User ID of last updater |

#### Access by Role

| Operation | SUPER_ADMIN | ADMIN |
|-----------|:-----------:|:-----:|
| Read | ✅ | ❌ |
| Write | ✅ | ❌ |

