### 4. Lead

Each lead belongs to one **ADMIN** directly (via `adminId`).
There is no intermediate CLIENT owner.

| Field | Type | Notes |
|-------|------|-------|
| `id` | String (UUID) | PK |
| `adminId` | String (FK → User.id) | Owner — the ADMIN this lead belongs to |
| `name` | String | Lead full name |
| `phone` | String | Validated: 10–15 digits |
| `email` | String? | Optional |
| `city` | String? | Optional |
| `source` | Enum (LeadSource) | See enums below |
| `status` | Enum (LeadStatus) | See enums below |
| `remarks` | String? | Internal notes |
| `whatsappOptIn` | Boolean | Default: false |
| `createdAt` | DateTime | Auto |
| `updatedAt` | DateTime | Auto |

**No `followUpDate` or `reminderSent` fields** — follow-up scheduling is handled by the FollowUp table.

**Unique constraint**: `(adminId, phone)` — same phone can exist across different admins, not within the same admin.

**Indexes**: `adminId`, `status`, `phone`, `createdAt`

**Cascade**: deleted when parent User (ADMIN) is deleted.

#### Access by Role

| Operation | SUPER_ADMIN | ADMIN |
|-----------|:-----------:|:-----:|
| Read all leads system-wide | ✅ | ❌ |
| Read own leads (`adminId` = self) | ✅ | ✅ |
| Create leads | ✅ | ✅ |
| Edit leads | ✅ | ✅ (own only) |
| Delete leads | ✅ | ✅ (own only) |
| Export leads | ✅ | ✅ (own only) |

