### 6. ActivityLog

Audit trail. Written on every meaningful state change — never written by keep-alive cron or system health checks.

| Field | Type | Notes |
|-------|------|-------|
| `id` | String (UUID) | PK |
| `userId` | String? (FK → User.id) | Who triggered the action (null for webhook/system) |
| `leadId` | String? (FK → Lead.id) | Affected lead (null for non-lead actions) |
| `action` | String | See action strings below |
| `details` | JSON? | `{ oldValue, newValue, metadata }` |
| `createdAt` | DateTime | Auto |

**Standard action strings:**
`CREATE_LEAD`, `UPDATE_LEAD`, `DELETE_LEAD`, `UPDATE_STATUS`,
`FOLLOW_UP_CREATED`, `FOLLOW_UP_COMPLETED`, `FOLLOW_UP_SNOOZED`, `FOLLOW_UP_CANCELLED`,
`SEND_WHATSAPP_REMINDER`, `SEND_EMAIL_REMINDER`,
`WHATSAPP_LEAD_CAPTURED`, `ADMIN_CREATED`, `ADMIN_SUSPENDED`

**Indexes**: `userId`, `leadId`, `createdAt`

#### Access by Role

| Operation | SUPER_ADMIN | ADMIN |
|-----------|:-----------:|:-----:|
| Read all logs | ✅ | ❌ |
| Read own logs (`userId` = self, or leads where `adminId` = self) | ✅ | ✅ |

