## What This Schema Does NOT Have (intentional)

| Missing Field | Reason |
|---------------|--------|
| `Lead.followUpDate` | Replaced by FollowUp table |
| `Lead.reminderSent` | Replaced by `FollowUp.reminderSentAt` |
| `Lead.clientId` | Leads belong to ADMIN directly, field is `adminId` |
| `User.adminId` | No parent-child User hierarchy in V1 |
| `SystemSettings.whatsappToken` | Per-admin config lives in AdminSettings |
| `WhatsAppChannel` model | V2 multi-channel feature — not in V1 |
| `channelId` on Lead | V2 only |
